Dialogue: 0,0:22:48.46,0:22:51.46,EDTC,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\blur3}夜晚就此開幕
Dialogue: 0,0:22:51.68,0:22:53.01,EDTC,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\blur3}讓我們
Dialogue: 0,0:22:53.25,0:22:57.02,EDTC,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\blur3}雙手打著拍子 此起彼落地
Dialogue: 0,0:22:57.43,0:23:01.83,EDTC,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\blur3}邊開懷大笑邊放聲高歌
Dialogue: 0,0:23:01.83,0:23:05.39,EDTC,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\blur3}連藏在心中的眼淚
Dialogue: 0,0:23:05.49,0:23:09.24,EDTC,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\blur3}也溶入了傳來傳去的酒杯
Dialogue: 0,0:23:10.24,0:23:12.13,EDTC,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\blur3}無論邂逅的人
Dialogue: 0,0:23:12.32,0:23:14.05,EDTC,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\blur3}或是訣別的夢
Dialogue: 0,0:23:14.39,0:23:18.29,EDTC,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\blur3}都是這再真實不過的人生
Dialogue: 0,0:23:18.29,0:23:22.28,EDTC,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\blur3}置身這片愛中 引吭高歌
Dialogue: 0,0:23:22.28,0:23:25.93,EDTC,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\blur3}盡情乾杯吧
Dialogue: 0,0:23:26.43,0:23:32.01,EDTC,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\blur3}敬那一天又一天的冒險
